data.description: Single-story gem nestled on Stallion Mountain Golf Course, a 55+ community in Henderson. A golfer's paradise, this residence boasts breathtaking views of the golf course from every angle. Featuring 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, plus a versatile den that can easily serve as a 3rd bedroom, this home exudes both style and functionality. The master bedroom is a retreat in itself, showcasing a HUGE walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with double sinks. The kitchen is a culinary delight, adorned with granite countertops and equipped with SS appliances that are yours to keep. The backyard faces Hole 15, and offers a covered patio and ceiling fan to enjoy the view with comfort. Situated within a DOUBLE Guard Gated community, this home ensures security and privacy. The exclusive amenities of the clubhouse include tennis courts, pool & spa, and fitness center. This home is energy efficient, with Solar through Solar City! Located under 10 miles from the Strip & Airport!
